ladspa-riaa (1.2.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Save all plugin settings to configuration file
  * Added declick settings persistence (enable, threshold, width)
  * Added notch filter settings persistence (enable, frequency, Q factor)
  * Saved settings now automatically load on plugin startup
  * Configuration values override LADSPA port hint defaults
  * Fixed NULL pointer handling for unconnected control ports
  * All 9 user-adjustable parameters now persist across sessions

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Sat, 01 Feb 2026 18:00:00 +0000

ladspa-riaa (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Changed configuration file location from ~/.config to ~/.state
  * Added priority.driver = 1 to PipeWire configuration

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Sat, 01 Feb 2026 12:00:00 +0000

ladspa-riaa (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * RIAA phono preamp equalization plugin
  * LADSPA plugin format
  * Subsonic filtering with 1st and 2nd order options
  * Adjustable gain control
  * Declick feature for vinyl pop/click removal
  * Notch filter for mains hum removal
  * Command-line processing utility
  * Configuration file support
  * PipeWire configuration for automatic turntable routing
  * WirePlumber rules for ALSA input connection

 -- HiFiBerry <support@hifiberry.com>  Thu, 30 Jan 2026 12:00:00 +0000
